[1
Date: Thu, 14 May 1998 10:00:48 -0400
From: D. W. MacPherson <dmacpher@fhs.csu.mcmaster.ca>

Here is a reference of primary work done on heat decontamination of water
done in our laboratory. This article is accompanied by an excellent
editorial review by Dr. Howard Baker.
Groh CD, MacPherson DW, Groves DJ. Effect of heat on the sterilization of
artificially contaminated water. J Travel Med 1996; 3: 11-13.
--
D. W. MacPherson MD, MSc(CTM), FRCPC
Director, Regional Parasitology Laboratory
St. Joseph's Hospital / McMaster University
Hamilton, Ontario, CANADA L8N 4A6
