From: David Birnbaum <brnbaum@unixg.ubc.ca>

In as much a question as an answer, one comprehensive index to such
information is:
Mitscherlich E, Marth EH (eds)
MICROBIAL SURVIVAL IN THE ENVIRONMENT
1984, Springer-Verlag, Berlin
I don't have a copy handy, but wonder if: (1) it contains sufficient
information to answer your question; (2) list members know of more recent
compendiums of the same nature.
--
David Birnbaum, PhD, MPH
Clinical Assistant Professor
Dept. of Health Care & Epidemiology
University of British Columbia, Canada
