[3
Date: Thu, 14 May 1998 11:34:21 -0400
From: Walter Jakubowski <waterbug@worldnet.att.net>

In response to the above item, the moderator (mhj) requested information on
boil water advice for inactivating microorganisms. Please see the Morbidity
and Mortality Weekly Report (MMWR), September 16, 1994, Vol. 43, No. 36,
pp. 662-663 and 669.
This publication discusses boiling times for waterborne bacteria, viruses
and protozoa and provides a list of references.
--
Walter Jakubowski
WaltJay Consulting
Cincinnati, Ohio 45230
e-mail: waterbug@worldnet.att.net
